{"tid":1132413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉陳同佳案庭上拍照　內地女學生欲回國考試　官信懷熱誠准離境","createTime":"2019-04-30T09:40:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T13:11:28.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c4da0fa39d7f55e735998dbccac786d812554ff3","tid":1132413,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:40:23.000Z","msg":"於北京主修法律的內地女學生昨於高等法院旁聽陳同佳案判刑，涉嫌於庭內拍照及錄影，被控一項在法庭內攝影罪。裁判官今（30日）早准她保釋但拒絕讓她離境，惟女事主稱考試在即，想回國應考。裁判官下午再作考慮，認為她懷有熱誠，想探索社會及兩地法庭的分別，惟忽略了當中的規矩，最終准她以100元作保釋金，撤銷不准離港的條款，並將提訊日子押後至6月12日，又叮囑她緊記準時出庭。<br />\n被告在北京主修法律<br />\n<br />\n被告趙浦伊，19歲，報稱學生。她被指昨日於高等法院10樓第24庭拍下6張相片及2段影片。<br />\n<br />\n被告下午獲當值律師酌情代表出庭。裁判官提及被告在北京主修法律，欲參觀本港法庭。官續詢問她何時考試，被告稱即將考試，下月中考完，6月放假。<br />\n官指或忽略了規矩<br />\n<br />\n控方表示無基礎指被告持惡劣意圖在庭內拍攝，另當時旁聽案件人數眾多，塞滿法庭，被告是在判刑後才入內拍照。控方不反對保釋。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官認為，修讀法律的年輕被告懷有熱誠，想探索社會及兩地法庭的分別，但忽略了當中的規矩，最終撤銷今早不准她離港的保釋條件，只要求她交100元保釋金。法官又將案件改為於6月12日再訊，並著被告緊記準時出庭。"},{"pid":"fc9a9c8771d90a82b132c80e939eaeee870e4229","tid":1132413,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:41:30.000Z","msg":"100蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0730da0bd0f9e29cf49c78bba1595f7695733c6c","tid":1132413,"uid":152476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:41:51.000Z","msg":"又最後武士"},{"pid":"982c23621653384edbdbcc68a37ea074b31e4cd0","tid":1132413,"uid":38904,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:43:01.000Z","msg":"100蚊當豪俾狗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"015f9adc86181d9a82bfaeefa20c8e3585640856","tid":1132413,"uid":52276,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:43:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 熱誠？點止呀，熱愛祖國添呀"},{"pid":"860b057e6402fca53b4a89f9ea669452fcf79a9e","tid":1132413,"uid":88862,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:45:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c8e215d7ca61f5f47a81d75f8561adbbe0a615ad","tid":1132413,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:45:33.000Z","msg":"Hello Moro"},{"pid":"390b8b8a56bd7c3bda220ed1326af952d6c27153","tid":1132413,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8e215d7ca61f5f47a81d75f8561adbbe0a615ad","tid":1132413,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:45:33.000Z","msg":"Hello Moro"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:45:51.000Z","msg":"Moto"},{"pid":"477acb0d78cf255a066571922f34f0b3baf86190","tid":1132413,"uid":41154,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:46:26.000Z","msg":"好快發現兩地法庭冇乜分別"},{"pid":"c9d2cc2ec50086dbb5c63176aade228be113dafe","tid":1132413,"uid":66569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:52:35.000Z","msg":"留名6月跟進"},{"pid":"fe9f172da922044e2cc76d630dbac040ac3bf83f","tid":1132413,"uid":218466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:53:55.000Z","msg":"陳庭佳陳庭佳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dc58c0c960feeb791b87e51e9a86006740bf947","tid":1132413,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:59:55.000Z","msg":"天真的法官"},{"pid":"22bd2b4db9cdf60a0917ce1572763fd6dad91160","tid":1132413,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T10:01:51.000Z","msg":"反對派集體去影相啦屌"},{"pid":"0949659718aa576a3c7f31cf9090b5ae38619809","tid":1132413,"uid":14103,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T10:11:04.000Z","msg":"屌你老味 佔中果幾個有邊個冇熱誠"},{"pid":"7f8dff8499